We do not offer the App or any Services to children under 16 years of age. Users of the App and our Services are asked to confirm their date of birth as part of the registration process. Any user who indicates that they are under 16 years of age will not be able to use the App or our Services. If you believe that your child has provided a false date of birth to use the App or our Services, please let us know by contacting us at privacy@SoLoud.com.
